    <h1 class="mb-6">Google AI Optimisation UK</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google AI Overviews appear at the top of search results, replacing traditional links with AI-generated answers. Gemini is Google's AI assistant. Google AI Mode is the new dedicated AI search tab. All three pull from different combinations of signals - but all favour businesses with strong presence across Google's own infrastructure.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Rank4AI builds your presence across 20+ Google-owned platforms. When content is published there, it does not need to be discovered. It is already inside the system Google AI Overviews and Gemini draw from.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">For the full guides, see <a href="/learn/guides/google-ai-overview-optimisation/" class="link">Google AI Overview Optimisation</a> and <a href="/learn/guides/google-ai-mode/" class="link">Google AI Mode Optimisation</a>.</p>
